<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>Posts on Biographies-of-Ura</title><link>http://localhost:1313/posts/</link><description>Recent content in Posts on Biographies-of-Ura</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="http://localhost:1313/posts/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title/><link>http://localhost:1313/posts/%E6%AF%8F%E5%91%A8%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E8%AE%B0%E8%BD%BD%E8%A1%A8-%E7%AC%AC2%E5%91%A8/</link><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/%E6%AF%8F%E5%91%A8%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E8%AE%B0%E8%BD%BD%E8%A1%A8-%E7%AC%AC2%E5%91%A8/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;防烫伤&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;近期天气极寒，不少同学会应用铁氧化成三氧化二铁并放出热量的原理取暖，但因缺乏安全知识，直接在皮肤上取暖，结果导致真皮层永久性损伤。所以千万注意不要过度保暖，否则容易脱皮&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title/><link>http://localhost:1313/posts/%E6%AF%8F%E5%91%A8%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E8%AE%B0%E8%BD%BD%E8%A1%A8-%E7%AC%AC1%E5%91%A8/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/%E6%AF%8F%E5%91%A8%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E8%AE%B0%E8%BD%BD%E8%A1%A8-%E7%AC%AC1%E5%91%A8/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;防感冒&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;近期天气严寒，不少同学因衣物增加不及时导致感冒，同时并发还有诺如病毒、新冠病毒等，很容易同时感染多种疾病住进ICU。所以千万注意保暖，否则有生命危险&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>